{
  "stem": "7683.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, although I didn't have any direct experience, bad experience with not-Jewish, but there was, for example, sections in Lodz where I lived where I wouldn't go as a Jew there because the anti-Semitism was in there.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was told, don't go there because there is not a Jew goes there, things like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just because that was strict not-Jewish area, and there were very big anti-Semites.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I really cannot remember that I have some bad experience by myself-- by myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All my friends were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not really friend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I would assume-- we were together in these different mixtures of-- you had some people which you liked more than others.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not a special friendship with, because the circumstances didn't bring it to be more friendly with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I don't remember any special-- I know a few friends what I had, they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what I say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But not really a-- a close-- close connection with not-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was it a problem for you, being a Jew in the Polish army and trying to-- were you trying to be observant in any kind of way?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was not observant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't have any problems with being just a Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you always kept far away, because the air-- atmosphere was very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Matter of fact, right on the front, I was more afraid for the Polish citizens and the Polish friends than for the Germans, because you were afraid.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had a reservation about not to be too close with them because you didn't trust them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Didn't trust them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- so we-- we'd be so-- a danger more that they can shoot you.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
